data.description: Let your imagination run free as your step into this beautiful home and start thinking about where you will place your furniture! Wonderful floor plan with high ceilings, spacious kitchen that opens to the breakfast and living area ~ primary suite located downstairs with all secondary rooms upstairs along with a large game room and media room with endless possibilities! Conveniently located to schools, Alamo Ranch Shopping Center, NW Vista College, Sea World, UTSA, the Shops at La Cantera, The Rim and much more...Spacious backyard that also features a 20 X 10 covered patio to enjoy great times with friends and family ~ come check out this beautiful home today!
